sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant A as agent
    participant P as prepare_search
    participant E as search_embed
    participant H as search_hybrid
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant R as rerank
    participant A2 as agent

    U->>A: Follow-up request
    Note over A: Sees CURRENT SHORTLIST and prior messages
    A->>P: search_companies tool call
    P-->>E: normalized search state
    E-->>H: embedding or skip
    H->>DB: Hybrid retrieval or shortlist filtering
    DB-->>H: raw company rows
    H-->>R: shortlist
    Note over R,A2: summarize_search packages the ToolMessage summary
    R-->>A2: filtered shortlist summary
    A2-->>U: Final analysis
